freemarker.template.utility

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • freemarker.template.utility.Constants

  • public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    Frequently used constant TemplateModel values.

    These constants should be stored in the TemplateModel sub-interfaces, but for backward compatibility they are stored here instead. Starting from FreeMarker 2.4 they should be copied (not moved!) into the TemplateModel sub-interfaces, and this class should be marked as deprecated.
